snippet: Clerical workers at the ports of Los Angeles and Long Beach and the terminal operating companies that employ them agreed to federal mediation in an attempt to bring a labor dispute to an end.
abstract: Clerical workers at ports of Los Angeles and Long Beach and the terminal operating companies that employ them agree to federal mediation in an attempt to bring a labor dispute and strike to an end.
lead_paragraph: Clerical workers at the ports of Los Angeles and Long Beach and the terminal operating companies that employ them agreed to federal mediation in an attempt to bring a labor dispute to an end.
